answersResultList.title: You are very dark.
answersResultList.resultContent: People speak in hushed voices when you're around, assuming you've just come from a funeral. If you're young enough, they might assume satanic worship or grave robbing. Your happy face is just plain creepy, and you can clear a room by laughing. All this misunderstanding just amplifies your inner pain. Which is, of course, a good thing.
